item.title: Making F2P money
item.dc:creator: @haticks haticks
item.description:
@haticks wrote:

Vials of water. Buy 1k vails in GE, fill them up (takes like 20-30 mins) Then sell The Vials of Water in the GE for more. Works because members are buying the filled ones for herbalore. Writing a script for it wouldn’t be that hard either.

Jmacro has a script for it, or you can just go back and forth.
I made 200k in around 2 hours.
